<collectingCountry id="F35940EAFFE033093195DFA6FE9510B0" box="[151,286,1196,1222]" name="Philippines" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Philippines</collectingCountry>
, Talaud Islands, Sulawesi, and Timor in the east (for further information see below).
</paragraph>
